Build-mode marker (DEC-BUILD-005). While this file exists, the MAIN SESSION may
write to protected paths that the build itself must author (.claude/agents,
.claude/skills, schemas, workflows, evaluations/rubrics, project scaffolds).
Subagents are fully enforced regardless. docs/architecture/** and all secret
paths are denied in every mode.

This file is REMOVED at slice acceptance (step 6) — its deletion is part of the
acceptance commit, flipping the main session to full runtime enforcement.
